# =============================================================================
# WorldExplorer — muhit o'zgaruvchilari (namuna)
# =============================================================================
# Bu faylni nusxalab .env.local yarating va haqiqiy qiymatlarni kiriting.
# .env.local git'ga kirmaydi — maxfiy kalitlar xavfsiz saqlanadi.
#
#   cp .env.example .env.local   (Mac/Linux)
#   copy .env.example .env.local (Windows)
# =============================================================================

# REST Countries v5 API kaliti (MAJBURIY — production uchun)
# Bepul kalit: https://restcountries.com/sign-up
  =

# =============================================================================
# Vercel deploy
# =============================================================================
# 1. GitHub repozitoriyani Vercel'ga ulang
# 2. Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# 3. Quyidagi o'zgaruvchini qo'shing:
#      Name:  REST_COUNTRIES_API_KEY
#      Value: (restcountries.com dan olingan kalit)
#      Environment: Production, Preview, Development
# 4. Redeploy qiling
#
# Eslatma: NEXT_PUBLIC_ prefiksi bilan boshlanadigan o'zgaruvchilar
# brauzerga ochiladi. API kalitlariga HECH QACHON NEXT_PUBLIC_ qo'shmang.
